description: Waffling Around began back in 2001 as a Boba shop with a small menu. After an amazing response from the public, they decided to expand their delicious Wafflepops, Boba and now Koi Parfaits to a greater selection of customers by participating in events, festivals and private parties. If your taste buds are in dire need of some sweet treats then check out Waffling Around today!
name: Waffling Around
